{"tid":425940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本買樓廿萬有交易","createTime":"2017-10-06T07:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T04:04:11.000Z","uid":50502,"like":19,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"a1a05e360e9a07efc2b371c9f5efdc35b70375de","tid":425940,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"離jr 站10min 廿幾萬港紙買到 full paid <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n計返香港差唔多條件既樓 賣緊$500萬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n揸住五球 日本買完樓仲有四百幾萬揸手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拎去做定期5%pa 計利息都每月有萬四入你袋 而香港買完樓你就只有樓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697495a0ff477c0f8a5af850ec05702042b15dfc","tid":425940,"uid":50502,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3ed5d2a0f8f79402f602e5f9ebd8db274a83b9","tid":425940,"uid":148264,"like":2,"dislike":124,"score":-122,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:34:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51434bc9dc8125d1f52b3f7cc3487fb8239bb80f","tid":425940,"uid":997,"like":87,"dislike":5,"score":82,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:37:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解日本人成日候住中國人既領土 <span style=\"color: red;\">搶中國既釣魚台</span> 點解？就係因為中國太好</blockquote><br />\n果度叫尖閣諸島, 從來都唔係支那人"},{"pid":"5f6b5cf38622cbb8ab529bc086c29f8f1a13a037","tid":425940,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"eba33b4e40e9edf8d17a38645c32817ebdd28193","tid":425940,"uid":148264,"like":3,"dislike":84,"score":-81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:39:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bdcbc8e971f5cd6995636fa17096c6739da7d45","tid":425940,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:40:52.000Z","msg":"問題你買黎除左放租就無用"},{"pid":"5a4a6eea708b61fe009b26ea40644e3887698775","tid":425940,"uid":148264,"like":2,"dislike":29,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:41:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除